text: Bailampudi is a 2019 Indian Telugu language film written and directed by Anil Pg Raj and produced by Bramhananda Reddy. The film stars Harish Vinay and Tanishq Rajan in lead roles, with Bramhananda Reddy in prominent role. The music was composed by Subhash Anand. ==Plot== Witness intense family drama, village politics for power and vengeance at its peak. The story depicts the battle to survive, not to win in the game of life. == Cast == * Harish Vinay * Tanishq Rajan * Bramhananda Reddy ==Marketing and release== The shooting was completed in a deep-rooted village with minimal makeup used for the artists, including the heroine to maintain the rawness intact. The first song of the film was released on 9 January 2019. == References == ==External links== * Category:2019 films Category:Indian drama films Category:Telugu-language films Category:Indian films Category:2010s Telugu-language films Category:2019 drama films
